\r\n\tThis organic body wash for your baby contains natural ingredients such as olive oil and chamomile. Olive oil is a natural moisturiser

so it is safe on your little one’s skin.

Directions for Use

  • Dispense an adequate amount of this body wash onto your palm.

  • Rinse well with water.
